.social/@k4tj4" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;k4tj4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Chris Barnes&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="h-card"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://mastodon.world/@clbarnes" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;clbarnes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Bruno Vellutini&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="h-card"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://mastodon.social/@bruvellu" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;bruvellu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Marc Corrales &lt;span class="h-card"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://qoto.org/@Corralesmarc" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;Corralesmarc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110352718502111528</guid><pubDate>Thu, 11 May 2023 23:47:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Nicole Rust</title><link>https://neuromatch.social/@NicoleCRust/110350423327763561</link><description>Starting a list of all the amazing early career researchers that have made the wise decision to join us on this worthy platform (but might also take an exposure hit for that). Let's all boost and follow!  Let me start with two:&lt;span class="h-card"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://mastodon.social/@WorldImagining" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;WorldImagining&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="h-card"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://fediscience.org/@kinleyid" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;kinleyid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Please add two more (maybe yourself and 1 other?)</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110352726616411848</guid><pubDate>Thu, 11 May 2023 23:49:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Spencer LaVere Smith</title><link>https://neuromatch.social/@sls/110353978670952795</link><description>Bob Goldstein